summary:
The Security Council:

Recalling previous relevant resolutions and statements, 

Established a Panel of Experts to monitor sanctions on proliferation of nuclear, chemical, and biological weapons,

Decides to:

1. Extend the Panel's mandate until 5 April 2015, review it by 5 March 2015;
2. Request midterm report by 5 August 2014, final report by 5 February 2015, 
   and submit to Council after discussion with Committee;
3. Request Panel to provide program of work within 30 days, 
   and regular updates;
4. Continue following Panel's work;
5. Urge cooperation with Committee and Panel; 
6. Remain seized of the matter.
